to christen my jet ski,

00:00:39.205 --> 00:00:41.641
so we got the HMS
Rebecca O'Malley

00:00:41.641 --> 00:00:44.444
and the HMS Kill Rock Stars.

00:00:44.444 --> 00:00:45.712
And then,

00:00:45.712 --> 00:00:47.147
0.05 miles

00:00:47.147 --> 00:00:49.516
into the 1,000 mile trip

00:00:49.516 --> 00:00:53.686 align:start size:97% position:3%
and we hit a lock, and
we're stuck for three hours.

00:00:54.621 --> 00:00:57.757
