intended for divorced dads

00:01:27.854 --> 00:01:30.990
to get drunk on, while still
seeming cool to their kids.

00:01:30.990 --> 00:01:32.192
(laughter)

00:01:32.192 --> 00:01:33.793
(signal horn blares)

00:01:33.793 --> 00:01:37.030 align:start size:94% position:6%
- We're good.
- We're back on the road!

00:01:38.965 --> 00:01:42.635
