beginning of my trip.

00:02:03.223 --> 00:02:06.092
And we're sending 500 goats
and 1000 chickens to Africa.

00:02:06.092 --> 00:02:08.995
Thank you so much
for your support.

00:02:18.738 --> 00:02:19.806
Safety first!

00:02:22.375 --> 00:02:23.676
Start point.

00:02:23.676 --> 00:02:25.345
Ground zero.

00:02:25.345 --> 00:02:26.980
Not in the 9/11 sense

00:02:26.980 --> 00:02:30.150 align:start size:88% position:13%
but just in the sense
that I'm beginning here.

00:02:30.150 --> 00:02:33.586
(plaintive Latin guitar)

