of Chicago, guys,

00:03:02.682 --> 00:03:07.420
very quickly it becomes
an industrial wasteland.

00:03:07.420 --> 00:03:11.224
There's a homeless
man living in a tent!

00:03:11.224 --> 00:03:13.927
Like as soon as the
buildings fall away,

00:03:13.927 --> 00:03:17.197
it just goes from fields, to
gravel pits, to junkyards,

00:03:17.197 --> 00:03:19.999
to sand pits and back
to junkyards again.

00:03:19.999 --> 00:03:24.804
I'm not gonna lie, shit got
real depressing, real fast.

00:03:24.804 --> 00:03:27.207
And I'm the one who's
on the fun jet ski.

00:03:27.207 --> 00:03:28.474
